###############################
1 Descriptrion:
The script is for the kpt_utils test!

2 Usage:
Usage: perl kpt_utils_itp.pl <SHIM_AUTO_DIR> <CONF_FILE> <TYPE OF TESTING>

AUTO_DIR      : Path where all the scripts are placed

CONF_FILE     : Configuration File appended with path

TYPE OF TEST  : On Selecting Operation TYPE, This argument is mandator
                Eg: ALL, CLIENT, AGENT, WPK
Eg: perl  kpt_utils_itp.pl /home/automation/  kpt_utils.conf ALL



